The commercial foodservice market is segmented based on product type, end-users, and geography. In terms of product, the market is divided into food preparation equipment, drink preparation equipment, cooking equipment, and serving equipment. Food preparation equipment includes items like slicers, mixers, and peelers, while drink preparation equipment covers coffee machines and juicers. Cooking equipment consists of ovens, fryers, and grills, and serving equipment includes trays, display cases, and buffets. In terms of end-users, the market caters to full-service restaurants, quick-service restaurants, hotels & hospitality sector, hospitals & healthcare facilities, educational institutes, and others. Geographically, the market is analyzed across North America, Europe, Asia Pacific, Latin America, and the Middle East and Africa regions.

