**Global Commercial Foodservice Market**

The global commercial foodservice market is segmented by product type, end-users, and country. In terms of products, the market includes kitchen purpose equipment, refrigeration equipment, ware washing equipment, food holding and storing equipment, and other miscellaneous equipment. The end-user segment consists of full-service restaurants (FSR), quick-service restaurants (QSR), institutional users, and other foodservice establishments. The market is further analyzed based on country, including the United States, Canada, Mexico, Germany, Sweden, Poland, Denmark, Italy, the United Kingdom, France, Spain, the Netherlands, Belgium, Switzerland, Turkey, Russia, Japan, China, India, South Korea, New Zealand, Vietnam, Australia, Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia, the Philippines, Brazil, Argentina, the United Arab Emirates, Saudi Arabia, Oman, Qatar, Kuwait, South Africa, and other regions in Europe, Asia-Pacific, South America, and the Middle East and Africa.

